
VALUES('Žaklini Tatalović prećeno preko društvenih mreža', 'Novinarka N1 Žaklina Tatalović dobila je preteće poruke preko društvenih mreža. Tatalović je primila pretnje smrću i uvrede na račun njenog rada sa profila "Alma Begović" i "Sabo Zoltan". Pretnje su prijavljene policiji od strane Tatalović i UNS-a.', 'Serbian Journalist Threatened on Social Media', 'N1 journalist Žaklina Tatalović received threatening messages through social media.  Tatalović received death threats and insults about her work from the profiles “Alma Begović” and “Sabo Zoltan”. She reported the threats to the police. The journalists’ union UNS reminds that threats to journalists are unacceptable, and the authors of such content must be held responsible.', '2023-03-29', null, 2, 2, 1, '', '', '', 15, 2, 8, 7, null, null, 4, 29, null, null, 'https://www.uns.org.rs/sr/saopstenja/143328/uns-tuzilastvo-za-vtk-da-pronadje-ko-preti-smrcu-zaklini-tatalovic.html', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/DZb2R', '');

VALUES('Privatna tužba na račun BIRN Srbija', 'Gradonačelnik Aleksandar Šapić je tužio BIRN Srbija, glavnog i odgovornog urednika Milorada Ivanovića i novinare Jelenu Veljković, Aleksandra Đorđevića i Radmila Markovića zbog navodno iznetih neistina o njegovoj vili u Trstu i ozakonjenju gradnje na Bežanijskoj kosi. Tužbe su podnete zbog povrede časti, ugleda i ljudskog dostojanstva, a Šapić tvrdi da su iznete informacije prouzrokovale neizmernu štetu i povrede časti i ugleda.', 'BIRN Serbia Sued by Mayor for Damaging Reputation', 'Mayor Aleksandar Šapić has sued BIRN Serbia, the editor-in- chief Milorad Ivanović, and journalists Jelena Veljković, Aleksandar Đorđević, and Radmil Marković for allegedly spreading falsehoods about his villa in Trieste and the legalization of building on Bežanijska  Kosa. The lawsuits were filed for defamation and violations of honour, reputation, and human dignity. Šapić claims that the information caused immense harm and damage to his honour and reputation.', '2023-03-29', null, 2, 8, 1, '', '', '', 8, 6, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://birn.rs/sapic-tuzio-birn/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/jQpph', '');

VALUES('Sajt APR nedostupan usled tehničkog napada', 'Internet stranica i veb-server Agencije za privredne registre su bili meta napada Distributed Denial-of-Service (DDoS). Agencija je uspešno odbranila sistem u ponedeljak i omogućila pristup svim svojim veb-servisima, uz povremene prekide, a sistem sada nesmetano radi. Agencija je prijavila DDoS napade Nacionalnom centru za prevenciju bezbednosnih rizika u IKT sistemima (Nacionalni CERT) i Ministarstvu informisanja i telekomunikacija.', 'Serbia Business Agency Website Targeted by Technical Attack', 'The website and web server of the Business Registers Agency were targeted by Distributed Denial-of-Service DDoS attacks. The agency successfully defended the system on Monday and enabled access to all of its web services, with occasional interruptions, and the system is now operating smoothly. The agency reported the DDoS attacks to the National Center for the Prevention of Security Risks in ICT Systems, National CERT, and the Ministry of Information and Telecommunications.', '2023-03-27', null, 5, 2, 2, '', '', '', 9, 4, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.slobodnaevropa.org/a/sajt-apr-sajber-napad/32336304.html', 'https://apr.gov.rs/vesti.2428.html?newsId=3618', 'https://apr.gov.rs/vesti.2428.html?newsId=3618', '', 'https://archive.ph/F6C5c', 'https://archive.ph/dOhYQ');

VALUES('NDNV-u stigle pretnje na zvaničnu mejl adresu', 'Ekstremistički pokret "Konzervativni pokret Naši" poslao je pretnju na zvaničnu mejl adresu NDNV, optužujući organizaciju i portal Autonomija za to da su "strani plaćenici" koji vode "medijski rat protiv Rusije i Srbije" i "promovišu Ukrajinski neonacizam". U mejlu su posebno targetirali programskog direktora NDNV Dinka Gruhonjića i kolumnistu Autonomije Teofila Pančića.', 'Serbian Media and Journalists Threatened via Email', 'The extremist “Our Conservative Movement” sent a threat to the official email address of NDNV (Independent Journalists'' Association of Vojvodina) accusing the organization and the Autonomija portal of being “foreign mercenaries” who are waging a “media war against Russia and Serbia” and “promoting Ukrainian neo-Nazism”. The email specifically targeted NDNV’s program director Dinko Gruhonjić and Autonomija columnist Teofil Pančić. NDNV is calling on the authorities to investigate the organization that targets domestic media and organizations in favor of another state.', '2023-03-15', null, 2, 4, 1, '', '', '', 15, 7, 8, 7, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://ndnv.org/2023/03/16/ndnv-na-meti-ekstremista-institucije-da-sprece-fasizaciju-drustva/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/Xo0WR', '');

VALUES('Fišing kampanja sa lažnim e-računom Yettel-a', 'Fišing kampanja sa lažnim e-računom, logom i imenom kompanije Yettel kružila je na internetu. Iako je e-račun izgledao skoro identično kao računi Yettel-a, korisnici su upozoreni da obrate pažnju na domen.', 'Serbia Phishing Campaign Involves Fake e-invoice', 'A phishing campaign with a fake e-invoice, logo and name of Yettel company has been circulating on the internet in Serbia Although the e-invoice looked almost identical to Yettel’s invoices, users were warned to pay attention to the domain.', '2023-03-20', null, 3, 2, 2, '', '', '', 10, 32, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/dragan-jovanovi%C4%87-a4481627_ponovo-problemati%C4%8Dna-phishing-aktivnost-na-activity-7039563333691138048-fCro/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.ph/YZWHV', '');

VALUES('Pretnje Stevanu Dojčinoviću na Tik Tok-u', 'Istraživački novinar i urednik KRIK-a Stevan Dojčinović je govorio o životnom putu kriminalaca i regrutovanju mladića u navijačke grupe na podcastu Snaga uma. Nakon toga, na TikTok-u se pojavio komentar koji sugeriše da Dojčinovića treba ubiti. Ova javna pretnja ubistvom je prijavljena Posebnom tužilaštvu za borbu protiv visokotehnološkog kriminala.', 'Serbian Journalist Threatened with Death on Tik Tok', 'Stevan Dojčinović, an investigative journalist and editor- in-chief of KRIK, spoke about the life paths of criminals and the recruitment of young men into fan groups on the Snaga uma podcast. Following this, a comment appeared on TikTok suggesting that Dojčinović should be killed. This public death threat was reported to the Special Prosecution Office for High-Tech Crime.', '2023-03-07', null, 2, 2, 1, '', '', '', 15, 2, 8, 7, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://nova.rs/vesti/drustvo/stevan-dojcinovic-dobio-pretnje-ubistvom-nakon-gostovanja-na-nova-rs-slucaj-prijavljen/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/PGdDA', '');

VALUES('Narodnom poslaniku prećeno preko Fejsbuka', 'Šaip Kamberi, poslanik u Skupštini Srbije i šef poslaničke grupe „Ujedinjena dolina i SDA Sandžak“ dobio je pretnje smrću preko Fejsbuka od osobe koja se potpisuje kao Danijel Milković.', 'Serbian MP Threatened on Facebook', 'Šaip Kamberi, a Bosniak member of the Serbian parliament and head of the Jedinstvena dolina i SDA Sandžak parliamentary group, received death threats via Facebook from a person who introduced himself as Danijel Milković', '2023-02-25', null, 8, 4, 1, '', '', '', 15, 2, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://n1info.rs/vesti/kamberi-dobio-pretnje-smrcu-nikad-neces-znati-kada-dolazim-po-tvoju-glavu/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.ph/YMBE8', '');

VALUES('Lažni nalog Milana St. Protića na Tviteru', 'Napravljen je lažni nalog političara i diplomate Milana St. Protića na Tviteru. Protić uopšte nema otvoren nalog na tviteru.', 'Serbian Politician and Diplomat Impersonated on Twitter', 'A fake account of the politician and diplomat Milan St Protić has appeared on Twitter. Protić does not have an account on Twitter.', '2023-02-11', null, 6, 2, 1, '', '', '', 14, 11, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/strani_placenik/status/1624404461572456453', '', '', '', 'https://archive.ph/YGeSs', '');

VALUES('Protiv BIRN-a Srbija podneta je privatna tužba', 'BIRN Srbija našao se pred Višim sudom u Beogradu pošto je Vlasnik kompanije Jovanjica, podneo tužbu protiv BIRN-a pod tvrdnjom da su o njemu objavljenje neistine. BIRN Srbija smatra da ova tužba predstavlja pokušaj zastrašivanje medija kako ne bi pisali o određenim temama ili ličnostima.', 'Private Lawsuit Filed by Company Boss Against BIRN Serbia', 'BIRN Serbia found itself before the High Court in Belgrade after the owner of the company Jovanjica filed a lawsuit against BIRN claiming that untruths were published about him. BIRN Serbia believes the lawsuit represents an attempt to intimidate the media so that they do not write about certain topics or personalities.', '2023-02-13', null, 2, 8, 1, '', '', '', 8, 6, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://birn.rs/predrag-koluvija-tuzio-birn/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.ph/dP7xK', '');

VALUES('Pretnje upućene novinaru na Tviteru', 'Novinar portala Nova.rs Pero Jovović dobio je pretnje preko Tvitera. Slučaj je prijavio Tužilaštvu za visokotehnoločki kriminal. Udruženje novinara Srbije osudilo je pretnje.', 'Serbian Journalist Threatened on Twitter', 'Portal Nova.rs’ journalist Pero Jovović received threats via Twitter. He reported the case to the Prosecutor''s Office for High-Tech Crime. The Association of Journalists of Serbia condemned the threats.', '2023-02-09', null, 2, 4, 1, '', '', '', 15, 2, 4, 25, null, null, 4, 28, 4, 29, 'https://www.cenzolovka.rs/pritisci-i-napadi/jezive-pretnje-novinaru-peru-jovovicu-treba-ti-staviti-pistolj-na-celo-i-opaliti-metak-bez-trunke-savesti/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.is/5mOG7', '');

VALUES('Pretnje upućene novinarki preko Instagrama', 'Na Instagram nalog novinarke Radija 021 Gorice Nikolin upućen je niz uvreda i pretnji nakon što je objavila tekst o ateljeima na Petrovaradinskoj tvrđavi koji se kako se navodi u tekstu, nelegalno koriste.', 'Serbian Female Journalist Threatened on Instagram', 'Insults and threats were sent to the Instagram account of the journalist of the Radio 021, after she published an article about the studios at the Petrovaradin fortress, which, as stated in the article, are being used illegally.', '2023-01-31', null, 2, 4, 1, '', '', '', 15, 2, 8, 7, null, null, 4, 29, null, null, 'https://nuns.rs/nuns-procesuirati-pretnje-novinarki-gorici-nikolin/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/I4qI0', '');

VALUES('Portal Danas je objavio intervju sa nepostojećim ekspertom', 'Portal Danas objavio je intervju sa nepostojećom osobom. Naime lažni nalog Daniela Smith-a postojao je na Tviteru i imao je za cilj da širi različiti propagandni sadržaj. Nakon objavljenog teksta na portalu, nalog je Daniela Smith-a je obrisan.', 'Portal Danas Published Interview with Non-existent Expert', 'Portal Danas published an interview with a non-existent person. The fake account for Daniel Smith on Twitter aimed to spread various propaganda content. After the text was published on the portal, Daniel Smith’s account was deleted.', '2023-02-05', null, 3, 1, 1, '', '', '', 3, 15, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/frankblack2000/status/1621934449649745921?s=12&t=Z8pmNXycdRDEko4E2Z0cLQ', 'https://www.danas.rs/dijalog/licni-stavovi/sta-smo-naucili-iz-slucaja-daniel-smith/', 'https://www.danas.rs/dijalog/licni-stavovi/sta-smo-naucili-iz-slucaja-daniel-smith/', '', 'https://web.archive.org/web/20230206102011/https://twitter.com/frankblack2000/status/1621934449649745921?s=12&t=Z8pmNXycdRDEko4E2Z0cLQ', 'https://archive.li/oqYH3');

VALUES('Zloupotreba mejl adrese DZ Stara Pazova', 'Navodno u ime Doma zdravlja Stara Pazova i portala Moj doktor, građanima su stizali mejlovi sa zlonamernim / malicioznim prilozima sa ciljem da se zaraze računari građana.', 'Email address of Health Centre in Serbia Abused', 'Citizens received false malicious messages at the Stara Pazova Health Center and the My doctor portal as a part of a phishing campaign.', '2023-01-25', null, 3, 2, 2, '', '', '', 10, 32, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/ivanmarkovicsec/status/1618269721346068480', '', '', '', 'https://archive.ph/bk6RS', '');

VALUES('Aktivista priveden zbog svog tvita o predsedniku', 'Petar Đurić, predsednik udruženja građana „Pokret Ćale ovo je za tebe“ priveden je kako navodi njegov advokat nakon objave na Tviteru u kojoj kritikuje predsednika. Privela ga je Služba za borbu protiv organizovanog kriminala (SBPOK) i nakon ispitivanja pušten je na slobodu.', 'Serbian Activist Detained for Tweet About the President', 'Petar Đurić, President of the citizens’ association, was detained after posting a Tweet criticizing President Vucic. He was taken into custody by the Service for Combating Organized Crime SBPOK and released after questioning.', '2023-01-16', null, 1, 3, 1, '', '', '', 8, 6, 8, 9, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.danas.rs/vesti/politika/petar-djuric-priveden-u-sbpok-advokat-stojkovic-tvrdi-da-mu-nisu-dozvolili-da-ga-vidi/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.ph/TaEN6', '');

VALUES('Pretnje političarki preko Tvitera', 'Kopredsednica stranke Zajedno Biljana Stojković dobila je, kako navodi do sada najnajgrozniju pretnju u svojoj slikovitosti i namerama. Pretnju je dobila preko društvene mreže Tviter i slučaj je prijavila policiji.', 'Serbian Female Politician Threatened on Twitter ', 'The co-president of the Zajedno party, Biljana Stojković, reported receiving an alarming threat on Twitter and reported the case to the police.', '2023-01-16', null, 8, 2, 1, '', '', '', 15, 2, null, null, null, null, 4, 29, null, null, 'https://n1info.rs/vesti/biljana-stojkovic-prijavila-policiji-pretnju-smrcu/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.ph/WC8nD', '');

VALUES('Fišing kampanja sa brendom Pošte Srbije na Viberu', 'Na Tviter profilu @ivanmarkovicsec objavljeni su detalji fišing kampanje koja zloupotrebljava logotip Pošte Srbije. Poruke kruže po Viberu. Kako se navodi domen vaxvjhjxd[.]cyou je kupljen preko registra u Kini.', 'Phishing Campaign Abuses Serbian Post', 'Details of a phishing campaign that abuses the logo of the Post of Serbia were published on the Twitter profile of @ivanmarkovicsec. Messages are circulating on Viber. As stated, the domain vaxvjhjxd[.]cyou was purchased through a registry in China.', '2023-01-11', null, 3, 2, 2, '', '', '', 10, 32, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/ivanmarkovicsec/status/1613242320253747201?t=fEa4AlhWJt-mU2VjaLfEhg&s=35', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/BRcy3', '');

VALUES('Novinar iz Pirota priveden zbog izveštavanja o nesreći', 'Nenad Paunović, novinar iz Pirota, priveden je u policiju sa još jednom osobom nakon što su pokušali da dronom snime mesto nesrece i to u danu kada je bilo planirano podizanje oštećene cisterne na prugu. Nakon ispitivanja i četvrosatnog zadržavanja oni su pušteni.', 'Serbian journalist Detained for Filming Incident', 'Nenad Paunović, a journalist from Pirot, was questioned by police with one other person after trying to film an accident scene with a drone on the day it was planned to raise a damaged tank on the railway. After four hours in detention, they were released.', '2023-01-11', null, 2, 3, 1, '', '', '', 8, 6, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.cenzolovka.rs/pritisci-i-napadi/novinar-iz-pirota-povodom-privodjenja-zbog-snimanja-akcidenta-ne-mogu-da-mi-oproste-ministarku-i-mrtvog-turcina-koga-sam-nasao/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/CM9fd', '');

VALUES('DDoS napadi na sajtove državnih ministarstava', 'Po društvenim mrežama i medijima izašle su informacije o napadima na vebsajtove državnih institucija, konkretno: vojske, Min. odbrane, Min. spoljnih poslova, MUP-a, Aleksandra Vučića (vucic.rs).', 'DDoS Attacks on Websites of Serbian Govt Ministries Reported', 'There is information about attacks on the websites of state institutions, specifically the army, Defence Ministry, Foreign Ministry, MUP and President Aleksandar Vučić (vucic.rs) on social networks and in the media.', '2023-01-06', null, 5, 2, 2, 'https://archive.li/L2v44', '', '', 9, 4, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/ivanmarkovicsec/status/1610957828583219200?t=9h-ODE5wMC-fufFIZ-SicQ&s=35', 'https://twitter.com/ivanmarkovicsec/status/1611034259757613057?t=_lVNfVsSDlZESTlofIO9_g&s=35', 'https://twitter.com/ivanmarkovicsec/status/1611034259757613057?t=_lVNfVsSDlZESTlofIO9_g&s=35', 'https://www.slobodnaevropa.org/a/srbija-napadi-anonymous-institucije-sajtovi-serveri/32215930.html', 'https://archive.ph/IPGEj', 'https://archive.ph/M0kG5');

VALUES('Lažna nagradna igra navodno u ime kompanije Yettel', 'Kompanija Yettel obavestila je građane o lažnoj nagradnoj igri koja je kružila na sajtovima na internetu, konkretno je zabeležen maliziozni pop-up prozor na sajtu za konvertovanje YouTube videa u mp3 format. Navodno se nakon popunjavanja ankete, dobijaju vredne nagrade.', 'Yettel Warns of False Prize Game Scam', 'The company Yettel has informed citizens that a fake prize game is circulating on websites on the Internet. A malicious pop- up window was recorded on the site for converting YouTube videos to mp3 format. Apparently, after completing the survey, they receive valuable prizes.', '2023-02-27', null, 3, 2, 2, '', '', '', 10, 32, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7036256371142500352/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/mYzf9', '');

VALUES('Fišing kampanja usmerena na SBB korisnike', 'Početkom godine bila je aktivna fišing kampanja koja targetira SBB korisnike preko mejla, gde su korisnicima stizali lažni mejlovi sa obaveštenjem o navodnom problemu sa obnavljanjem usluga i upućivali ih na lažnu stranicu http://eunet.co.rs.', 'Phishing Campaign Targets SBB users in Serbia', 'At the beginning of the year, there was a phishing campaign targeting SBB users via email, where users received fake emails informing them of an alleged problem with renewing services and directing them to the fake page http://eunet.co.rs.', '2023-01-03', null, 3, 2, 2, '', '', '', 10, 32, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/ivanmarkovicsec/status/1610227799373086721?t=gVpNtg_P-fZqlMRqfd3Auw&s=35', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/34WlP', '');

VALUES('Lažni snimci masakra iz beogradske osnovne škole deljeni na društvenim mrežama', 'Nekoliko dana nakon masovne pucnjave u osnovnoj školi u Beogradu, TikTok-om su počeli da kruže snimci iz škole navodno snimljeni za vreme masakra. Brzo je otkriveno da je video zapravo prikazuje drugi incident koji se desio pre nekoliko godina u školi u Sjedinjenim Državama.', 'Fake footage of Belgrade school shooting circulated on social media', 'Days after a mass school shooting in Belgrade, footage started circulating on TikTok of alleged footage of the massacre from within the school. The video was quickly discovered to be from a different school shooting a couple of years back in the United States.', '2023-05-06', null, 3, 2, 1, '', '', '', 3, 12, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/mina_vrbaski/status/1654610887741784064', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/ckfyy', '');

VALUES('Pretnje novinaru zbog teksta o patrijarhu', 'Novinar dnevnog lista Danas Nikola Krstić dobio je brojne pretnje nasiljem na društvenim mrežama nakon što je napisao tekst o izjavi patrijarha Srpske pravoslavne crkve Porfirija. Krstić je u tekstu komentarisao uvredljivu izjavu koju je poglavar SPC uputio ženama u Srbiji.', 'Journalist threatened over article about the patriarch', 'Daily newspaper Danas'' journalist Nikola Krstić received numerous threats of violence on social networks after he wrote an article about the statement of the patriarch of the Serbian Orthodox Church, Porfirije. In the text, Krstić commented on the insulting statement that the head of the Serbian Orthodox Church made in relation to women in Serbia.', '2023-05-18', null, 2, 4, 1, '', '', '', 15, 2, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://kossev.info/safejournalist-zahteva-da-se-pronadju-osobe-koje-su-pretile-novinaru-lista-danas-nakon-teksta-o-patrijarhu-spc/', 'https://twitter.com/krkela_krle/status/1659113155413286912?s=20', 'https://twitter.com/krkela_krle/status/1659113155413286912?s=20', '', 'https://archive.li/yD8L3', 'https://archive.li/9RsDz');

VALUES('Istraživački portal osuđen zbog objavljivanja ko ih je tužio', 'Istraživački portal KRIK osuđen je prvostepenom presudom Višeg suda u Beogradu zbog objavljivanja teksta o tome ko je sve podnosio tužbe protiv ovog medija. Trojica pripadnika policije, koji su već podnosili tužbe i spominju se u tekstu, ponovo su tužili KRIK. Medij je već prvostepenom sudskom odlukom dužan da isplati skoro 3.200 evra na ime naknade štete za pretrpljenje duševne bolove, kao i da obriše delove teksta u kome se spominju pripadnici policije. KRIK je najavio da će se žaliti na presudu.', 'Investigative journalism portal sentenced for publishing the names of the plaintiffs who sued them', 'The investigative portal KRIK was convicted by a first-instance verdict of the High Court in Belgrade for publishing an article about who filed lawsuits against the media house. Three members of the police, who have already filed lawsuits and are mentioned in the text, sued KRIK again. The media is already obliged to pay almost 3,200 euros in compensation for suffering mental pain by the first-instance court decision, as well as to delete parts of the text in which members of the police are mentioned. KRIK announced that it will appeal the verdict.', '2023-05-18', null, 2, 3, 1, '', '', '', 8, 6, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.krik.rs/krik-osudjen-jer-je-objavio-ko-je-tuzio-redakciju-presudu-doneo-sudija-keranovic-poznat-po-procesu-protiv-nin-a/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/LcUKR', '');

VALUES('Portal Republika ugrozio privatnost porodica žrtava masakra', 'Tabloidni portal Republika je senzacionalističkim izveštavanjem sa sahrane ubijenih u masakru u okolini Mladenovca koji se desio 4. maja. Nezavisno udruženje novinara Srbije pozvalo je novinare da poštuje privatnost, dostojanstvo i integritet ljudi o kojima pišu, naročito kada je reč o tragedijama.', 'Portal Republika infringed on the privacy of the families of massacre victims', 'The tabloid portal Republika sensationally reported on the funeral of those killed in the massacre in the vicinity of Mladenovac that took place on May 4, thus violating the journalistic code and retraumatizing the families of the victims. The Independent Association of Journalists of Serbia called on journalists to respect the privacy, dignity and integrity of the people they write about, especially when it comes to tragedies.', '2023-05-09', null, 4, 6, 3, '', '', '', 7, 5, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://nuns.rs/nuns-portal-republika-da-postuje-kodeks-i-prava-na-privatnost-porodica-zrtava/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/99uCd', '');

VALUES('Brojne dezinformacije o ubistvima u školi u Beogradu', 'U danima nakon višestrukog ubistva u beogradskoj osnovnoj školi "Vladislav Ribnikar", na sajtovima medija u Srbiji i regionu i društvenim mrežama objavljene su brojne dezinformacije u vezi sa događajem. Između ostalog, prenete su netačne informacije da je i ranjena nastavnica preminula, da vakcinisani građani ne mogu da budu donatori krvi, kao i da je televizija N1 tražila puštanje na slobodu osumnjičenog.', 'Mass disinformation circulates about school shooting in Belgrade', 'In the days following the mass murders in Belgrade elementary school "Vladislav Ribnikar", numerous misinformation related to the event was published on media websites in Serbia and the region as well as on social networks. Among other things, incorrect information was conveyed that the wounded teacher also died, that vaccinated citizens could not be blood donors and that N1 television demanded the release of the suspect.', '2023-05-08', null, 3, 1, 1, '', '', '', 3, 15, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.cenzolovka.rs/mediologija/dezinformacije-o-masakru-u-skoli-vladislav-ribnikar/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/9lkDY', '');

VALUES('Narodna poslanica vladajuće stranke uputila uvrede poslanici opozicije na Tviteru', 'Narodna poslanica Staša Stojanović verbalno je napala zamenicu predsednika Demokratske stranke, isto narodnu poslanicu, Draganu Rakić na Tviteru nakon što je Rakić podelila video u kojem se vidi kako je Stojanović provocira u skupštini kao odgovor na protest dela opozicije na jučerašnjem zasedanju.', 'Ruling party MP insults opposition MP on Twitter', 'Serbian Progressive Party MP Staša Stojanović verbally attacked the deputy president of the Democratic Party and opposition MP Dragana Rakić on Twitter after Rakić shared a video showing Stojanović provoking her in the Assembly in response to a protest by the opposition at yesterday''s session.', '2023-05-25', null, 8, 8, 1, '', '', '', 4, 7, null, null, null, null, 4, 28, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/stasasns/status/1661776299877183490?s=46', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/14iY8', '');

VALUES('Preminuli srpski pevač pozvao preko Instagrama na SNS miting', 'Na Instagram nalogu poznatog srpskog pevača Šabana Šaulića objavljen je poziv za miting podrške predsedniku Aleksandru Vučiću i Srpskoj naprednoj stranci u Beogradu zakazan za 26. maj. Veliki broj javnih ličnosti podelio je poziv na svojim nalozima, ali je Šaulić jedini koji je to uradio posthumno.', 'Deceased Serbian singer posted on Instagram to invite people to SNS meeting', 'On famous Serbian singer Šaban Šaulić''s Instagram account, an invitation was published for a rally in support of President Aleksandar Vučić and the Serbian Progressive Party in Belgrade, scheduled for May 26. A large number of public figures shared the invitation on their accounts, but Šaulić was the only one who did so posthumously.', '2023-05-24', null, 3, 8, 1, '', '', '', 3, 12, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/NikolaLaki3/status/1661340279469744128', 'https://direktno.rs/vesti/drustvo-i-ekonomija/472153/saban-saulic-miting-vucic.html', 'https://direktno.rs/vesti/drustvo-i-ekonomija/472153/saban-saulic-miting-vucic.html', '', 'https://archive.li/hhfb8', 'https://archive.li/8Dd2e');

VALUES('Voditeljka dobila pretnje na svoj privatni broj', 'Olja Bećković, autorka i voditeljka emisije „Utisak nedelje“ dobila je na svoj privatni broj telefona uznemirujuće poruke od predsednika Udruženja porodica kidnapovanih, ubijenih i nestalih sa prostora Kosova i Metohije Sima Spasića.', 'Serbian TV Show Host Received Threats on Personal Number', 'Olja Bećković, author and host of the TV show “Utisak nedelje,” received disturbing text messages on her personal phone from Sime Spasić, the president of the Association of Families of Kidnapped, Murdered and Missing Persons from Kosovo and Metohija.', '2023-04-10', null, 2, 8, 1, '', '', '', 15, 2, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.danas.rs/vesti/drustvo/nisam-prijavila-ovo-nije-prvi-put-simo-spasic-pretio-i-olji-beckovic/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.ph/j4DkG', '');

VALUES('Voditelj dobio pretnje na privatni broj', 'Voditelj Ivan Ivanović primio je eksplicitne pretnje na privatni broj od predsednika Udruženja porodica kidnapovanih, ubijenih i nestalih sa prostora Kosova i Metohije Sima Spasića. Spasić je takođe uputio ozbiljne mizogine i eksplicitne pretnje članicama Ivanovićeve porodice. Spasić je uhapšen 19.06. zbog ugrožavanja sigurnosti voditelja.', 'TV host receives serious threats via SMS', 'TV host Ivan Ivanović received explicit threats on his private number from Simo Spasić, president of the Association of Families of Kidnapped, Murdered and Missing Persons from Kosovo and Metohija. Spasić also made serious misogynistic and explicit threats to members of Ivanović''s family. Spasić was arrested on June 19th. for endangering the hosts security.', '2023-04-09', null, 6, 8, 1, '', '', '', 15, 2, null, null, null, null, 4, 29, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/veceivan/status/1645172873055592448?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1645172873055592448%7Ctwgr%5E100438cb9068f82acf9c09eea99539560e35709a%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.danas.rs%2Fvesti%2Fdrustvo%2Fivanu-ivanovicu-i-njegovoj-porodici-vulgarne-pretnje-uputio-simo-spasic%2F', 'https://n1info.rs/vesti/uhapsen-simo-spasic-zbog-ugrozavanja-sigurnosti-ivana-ivanovica/', 'https://n1info.rs/vesti/uhapsen-simo-spasic-zbog-ugrozavanja-sigurnosti-ivana-ivanovica/', '', 'https://archive.li/9viel', 'https://archive.li/M8egA');

VALUES('Pevač pretio novinarima zbog teksta o njegovoj firmi', 'Pevač Vlado Georgiev pretio je novinarima Nova.rs koji su objavili tekst o njegovoj firmi ,,Dunav kargo'''' koju je otvorio 2020. godine i koja se bavi prevozom tereta unutrašnjim plovnim putevima. Objavili su istorijat firme i finansijske izveštaje.', 'Journalists Threatened Over Article on Cargo Company', 'Singer Vlado Georgijev threatened journalists from Nova.rs who published an article about his company Danube Cargo, which he opened in 2020 and deals with the transportation of cargo on inland waterways. They published the company’s history and financial reports.', '2023-04-10', null, 2, 5, 1, '', '', '', 15, 2, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://nova.rs/zabava/showbiz/trazicu-te-po-gradu-skandalozne-pretnje-vlada-georgieva-redakciji-nova-rs-nakon-pitanja-o-njegovom-biznisu/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.ph/SJ0nA', '');

VALUES('Novosti obrisale tekst o ambasadoru SAD', 'Večernje novosti su obrisale sa sajta tekst o ambasadoru SAD u Srbiji Kristoferu Hilu. Tekst je postao nedostupan iako se po internet pretrazi i agregatorima vesti vidi da je bio objavljen. U tekstu su pored detalja iz života ambasadora Hila navedene brojne negativne kvalifikacije o njegovom odnosu prema Srbiji i srpskom narodu. Novosti su poznate kao medij sa pretežno anti-zapadnom uređivačkom politikom.', 'Serbian News Portal Deletes Article on US Ambassador', 'Večernje novosti, a Serbian media outlet with a predominantly anti-Western editorial policy, deleted an article about the US ambassador to Serbia, Christopher Hill, from its website. The article has become unavailable although internet search and news aggregators show it was published. In addition to details from Hill’s life, the article contained negative remarks about his attitude towards Serbia and the Serbian people.', '2023-04-04', null, 3, 1, 1, '', '', '', 1, 27, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://n1info.rs/vesti/vecernje-novosti-objavile-pa-obrisale-pamflet-o-ambasadoru-kristoferu-hilu/', 'https://time.rs/c/179ed6dde6/diplomata-koji-ni-je-voleo-srbiju-mrznja-prema-srbima-pod-velom-maslinove-grancice.html', 'https://time.rs/c/179ed6dde6/diplomata-koji-ni-je-voleo-srbiju-mrznja-prema-srbima-pod-velom-maslinove-grancice.html', '', 'https://archive.li/CI6m6', 'https://archive.li/6w4Pe');

VALUES('Pevačica Jelena Karleuša vređala narodnu poslanicu Mariniku Tepić po nacionalnoj osnovi', 'Folk pevačica Jelena Karleuša je na svom Instagramu tažila od narodne poslanice Marinike Tepić da se izjasni o svojoj nacionalnoj pripadnosti, navodeći da u slučaju da se ne identifikuje kao srpkinja nema prava da učestvuje u protestima i kritikuje vlast jer ''ideološki'' ne pripada srpskom narodu. Pevačica je prethodno javno podržala predsednika Vučića i kritikovala umetrnike, prevashodno glumice i glumce zbog izražavanja negativnih stavova usmerenih prema vlasti i učestvovanja u protestima "Srbija protiv nasilja".', 'Singer Jelena Karleuša insulted MP Marinika Tepić on ethnic and national grounds', 'Folk singer Jelena Karleuša posted on her Instagram account demanding that MP Marinika Tepić declare her nationality, stating that if she does not identify as a Serb, she has no right to participate in protests and criticize the government because she is "ideologically" not a part of the Serbian people. The singer previously publicly supported President Vučić and criticized performers, primarily actresses and actors, for expressing negative attitudes towards the government and participating in the "Serbia against violence" anti-govenrment protests.', '2023-05-28', null, 8, 5, 1, '', '', '', 4, 47, 14, 7, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/amfibolije/status/1662834561221554181?s=46', 'https://twitter.com/charliewafflees/status/1663543162395320321?s=46', 'https://twitter.com/charliewafflees/status/1663543162395320321?s=46', '', 'https://archive.li/AXLKR', 'https://archive.li/NINrU');

VALUES('Nebojša Krstić fabrikovao fotografiju glumca Nikole Koje na Tviteru', 'Politički komentator Nebojša Krstić na svom Tviter profilu podelio je fotografiju glumca Nikole Koja sa protesta "Srbija protiv nasilja" održanog 27. maja. Kojo je na protestu nosio natpis sa imenom Majora Omera Mehića koji je 2015. godine stravično nastradao u padu helikoptera koji je ostao nerazjašnjen ali se spekuliše da je povezan sa nekompetencijom vlasti. Krstić je podelio fotografiju i zamenio ime na transparentu sa porukom "Srbi trpe nasilje na Kosovu". Krstić je već danima aktivan na Tviteru gde napada opoziciju i kritikuje proteste. ', 'Nebojša Krstić fabricated a photo of actor Nikola Koja on Twitter', 'Political commentator Nebojša Krstić shared a photo of actor Nikola Kojo from the "Serbia against violence" protest held on May 27 on his Twitter profile. At the protest, Kojo carried a sign with the name of Major Omer Mehić, who died terribly in a helicopter crash in 2015, which remains unexplained but is speculated to be connected to the incompetence of the authorities. Krstić shared the photo and replaced the name on the banner with the message "Serbs suffer violence in Kosovo". Krstić has been active on Twitter for days, where he attacks the opposition and criticizes the protests.', '2023-05-29', null, 6, 5, 1, '', '', '', 3, 12, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/CenzurisanoL/status/1663123104288190464?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1663221586021826560%7Ctwgr%5Eac34f6ca4d5296c5a26e9725546f7d3d47ec8da9%7Ctwcon%5Es3_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fnova.rs%2Fvesti%2Fpolitika%2Fnebojsa-krstic-probio-dno-kada-je-napao-nikolu-koja-stigao-je-snazan-odgovor-glumca%2F', 'https://citymagazine.danas.rs/scena/drustvene-mreze/nebojsa-krstic-je-pokusao-da-bude-drustveno-angazovan-i-duhovit/', 'https://citymagazine.danas.rs/scena/drustvene-mreze/nebojsa-krstic-je-pokusao-da-bude-drustveno-angazovan-i-duhovit/', '', 'https://archive.is/1lGMs', 'https://archive.li/jsBT2');

VALUES('Aktivista Lazar Pavlović našao se na meti homofobnih uvreda nakon protesta', 'Aktivista Gej strejt alijanse Lazar Pavlović, koji je na protestu "Srbija protiv nasilja" sa ženom i detetom šetao u majici "Lešinar tata" kao odgovor na način na koji je vlast okarakterisala demonstrante koji su šetali ulicama, već sutradan je napadnut na društvenim mrežama i u medijima. Pavlović je postao meta homofobnih napada pri čemu su takođe objavljivane i stare slike sa njegovog Instagram profila. ', 'Activist Lazar Pavlović was the target of homophobic insults following the protest', 'Activist of the Gay Straight Alliance, Lazar Pavlović, who walked with his wife and child at the "Serbia Against Violence" protest wearing a "Vulture Dad" t-shirt as a response to the way the authorities characterized the protesters who were walking in the streets, was attacked on social media and in the media the very next day. Pavlović became the target of homophobic attacks, with old pictures from his Instagram profile also being published.', '2023-05-28', null, 1, 1, 1, 'https://archive.li/61g5i', '', '', 14, 10, 4, 10, 4, 25, 6, 38, 1, 25, 'https://twitter.com/dasezna/status/1663167547569582080', 'https://www.politika.rs/sr/clanak/555094/Ko-je-Lazar-Pavlovic-koji-je-nosio-majicu-lesinar-tata', 'https://www.politika.rs/sr/clanak/555094/Ko-je-Lazar-Pavlovic-koji-je-nosio-majicu-lesinar-tata', 'https://twitter.com/DrugaSrbijaBis/status/1662702953554227200?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1662702953554227200%7Ctwgr%5E480e50488220ad2061f8085f9e56fb4eb2f42cc8%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alo.rs%2Fvesti%2Fpolitika%2F764869%2Fgej-i-opozicionar-po-potrebi-a-sad-postao-porodicni-covek-ko-je-lazar-pavlovic-i-sta-je-radio-na-protestu%2Fvest', 'https://archive.li/OGzKN', 'https://archive.li/bbU74');

VALUES('Lažni video vršnjačkog nasilja cirkulisao na TikToku nakon masovnog ubistva u osnovnoj školi', 'Nekoliko dana nakon masovne pucnjave u osnovnoj školi "Vladislav Ribnikar" u Beogradu, na TikToku se pojavio video koji navodno pokazuje učenike te škole kako maltretiraju ubicu uz komentare da video prikazuje trenutke pre masakra ili da je ovo samo primer tretmana koji je ubica doživljavao u školi. Brzo je otkriveno da je video zapravo iz škole u Rusiji i da je objavljen pre nekoliko meseci te da ni na koji način nije povezan sa tragedijom. Uprkos ovim saznanjima, video je masovno cirkulisao po društvenoj mreži i i dalje se nalazi na vise naloga koji izražavaju simpatije prema ubici. ', 'Fake bullying video circulated on TikTok after mass murder at elementary school', 'A few days after the mass shooting at the "Vladislav Ribnikar" elementary school in Belgrade, a video appeared on TikTok that allegedly shows the students of that school bullying the killer, with captions saying that the video shows the moments before the massacre or that this is just an example of the treatment the perpetrator was subject to at the school. It was quickly discovered that the video was actually from a school in Russia and had been released several months ago and was in no way connected to the tragedy. Despite this knowledge, the video circulated widely on the social network and can still be found on several accounts expressing sympathy for the killer.', '2023-05-06', null, 3, 2, 1, '', '', '', 3, 12, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://vm.tiktok.com/ZM22b3sJU/?t=2', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/cZ9UV', '');

VALUES('Presuda protiv udruženja građana zbog deljenja fotografije na Instagramu', 'Udruženje građana Fruškać izgubilo je pred Višim sudom u Beogradu prvostepeni spor po tužbi zbog deljenja fotografije na kojoj su bili tagovani putem Instagram storija. Udruženje je presudom obavezano da isplati 115.000 dinara na ime naknade štete za autorska prava i sudskh troškova, i najavilo žalbu na presudu. ', 'Judgment against citizens'' association for sharing a photo on Instagram', 'Citizens'' Association Fruškać lost a first-instance case before the High Court in Belgrade due to the sharing of a photo in which they were tagged via Instagram stories. The Association was obliged by the verdict to pay 115,000 dinars in the name of copyright damages and court costs and announced an appeal against the judgment.', '2023-05-30', null, 1, 4, 1, '', '', '', 8, 6, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=pfbid02TYFtgSgpHo1UEdZxwmWPvFD92DiXaTkf679Rf6guAVrVGUPvkfQYCw5m1SFzbQtxl&id=1008229337&mibextid=qC1gEa', '', '', '', '(screenshot)', '');

VALUES('Otkriveni lažni profili koji uznemiravaju žene na Instagramu', 'Na Instagramu su otkrivena dva lažna profila koji ženama šalju eksplicitne poruke. Na Tviteru se javio broj žena koji je dobio poruke sa ovih profila i neke su utvrdile da su fotografije korišćene na nalozima skinute sa interneta. Profili Aleksandar Božić i Popović Vlada predstavljaju se kao da su sa Pravoslavno bogoslovskog fakulteta u Beogradu.', 'Fake profiles harass women on Instagram', 'Two fake profiles that were sending explicit messages to women on Instagram have been discovered. A number of women who received messages from these profiles came forward on Twitter and some determined that the photos used on the accounts were taken off the Internet. The profiles of Aleksandar Božić and Popović Vlada present themselves as if they are members of the Faculty of Orthodox Theology in Belgrade.', '2023-04-05', null, 3, 2, 1, '', '', '', 15, 48, null, null, null, null, 4, 37, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/jasampicko_/status/1643712979412697088', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/Op9ca', '(screenshot 1&2)');

VALUES('Lažne dojave o bombama preko mejla', 'U utorak, 23. maja, nova serija anonimnih i lažnih dojava o postavljenim bombama pogodila je škole u Novom Sadu, Nišu, Kragujevcu, Kruševcu, Čačku i Gornjem Milanovcu. Prema podacima MUP-a tog dana je pristiglo čak 200 prijava o bombama. Policija je svaku dojavu proverila i utvrđeno je da su sve bile lažne. Takođe, dojave o bombama su stigle i na Vojno-medicinsku akademiju, Kliničko-bolnički centar Zvezdara, kao i Zoološki vrt u Beogradu. ', 'Anonymous and false bomb threat reports via email', 'On Tuesday, May 23rd, a new series of anonymous and false bomb threat reports targeted schools in Novi Sad, Niš, Kragujevac, Kruševac, Čačak, and Gornji Milanovac. According to the Ministry of Interior (MUP) data, there were even 200 reports of bomb threats received on that day. The police investigated each report and determined that they were all false. Additionally, bomb threats were also received by the Military Medical Academy, the Clinical Hospital Center Zvezdara, and the Belgrade Zoo.', '2023-05-17', null, 3, 2, 2, '', '', '', 10, 32, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.bbc.com/serbian/lat/svet-65619123', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/eUAnx', '');

VALUES('Sajt JUGpressa meta ozbiljnog napada', 'Sajt JUGpressa nedavno je bio izložen ozbiljnom napadu i pokušaju upada u njihov sistem, ali zahvaljujući brzoj reakciji njihovog tima za tehničku podršku, posledice su uspešno otklonjene. Ova medijska kuća već je ranije bila na udaru sličnih napada, što navodi na sumnju da je ovaj incident još jedan pokušaj vršenja pritiska zbog njihove objektivne, profesionalne i nepristrasne uređivačke politike. Sajt JUGpressa je bio još jednom pod tehničkim napadom 21. juna, i uspeli su da se oporave i posle ovog napada. ', 'JUGpress Website Successfully Defends Against Serious Cyber Attack', 'The website of JUGpress recently faced a significant attack and attempted breach of their system. However, thanks to the swift response of their technical support team, the consequences were successfully mitigated. This media organization has previously been targeted by similar attacks, raising suspicions that this incident is yet another attempt to exert pressure due to their objective, professional, and unbiased editorial policy. The JUGpress website was once again under a technical attack on June 21st, and they managed to recover successfully after this incident.', '2023-05-15', '2023-05-17', 2, 2, 2, 'https://archive.li/uESSY', '', '', 9, 4, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.facebook.com/ljiljana.stojanovic.1654/posts/pfbid02SyGkA7zyN5CcPTatfsi1U6FHN82LAhyeNcnh54TJ8YcRAnTAvPC1SWAiqVuJJQNYl', 'https://jugpress.com/sajt-regionalne-informativne-agencije-jugpress-ponovo-radi/', 'https://jugpress.com/sajt-regionalne-informativne-agencije-jugpress-ponovo-radi/', 'https://www.facebook.com/ljiljana.stojanovic.1654/posts/pfbid0R5yB6wSMisHip2dYfwkBg77RG1V8DDogZAt153a1VyXA2TbVdNXb7Mevt5Cou476l ', 'https://archive.li/DobTO', 'https://archive.li/yWAfM');

VALUES('Fišing kampanja koja targetira korisnike poštanskih usluga', 'Nacionalni CERT Republike Srbije upozorio je na novu fišing kampanju usmerenu na korisnike poštanskih usluga. Korisnicima se šalje lažna SMS poruka koja tvrdi da njihov paket nije mogao biti isporučen zbog navodno neplaćene carine, a poručuje im se da otvore link iz poruke koji vodi ka lažnoj stranici na kojoj se traži popunjavanje podataka o bankovnoj kartici. I time omogućava napadačima da preuzmu novac sa bankovnog računa korisnika.', 'Phishing Campaign Targeting Postal Service Users', 'The National Computer Emergency Response Team (CERT) of Serbia has issued a warning regarding a new phishing campaign targeting users of postal services. Users are receiving fraudulent SMS messages claiming that their package could not be delivered due to alleged unpaid customs fees. The message instructs them to open a link provided in the SMS, which redirects them to a fake webpage requesting their banking card information. By providing these details, attackers gain access to the users'' bank accounts and can steal their money.', '2023-05-10', null, 3, 2, 2, '', '', '', 10, 21, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.cert.rs/rs/obavestenje/1042-Fi%C5%A1ing-napadi-putem-SMS-poruka-na-korisnike-po%C5%A1tanskih-usluga.html', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/HczV2', '');

VALUES('Na Tviteru objavljena lažna ostavka ministarke', 'Na Tviteru se pojavila fotografija pisma ostavke Ministarke Rudarstva i Energetike Dubravke Đedović. Ubrzo je otkriveno da je pismo fabrikovano i da ministarka nije podnela ostavku. Na dokumentu je falio potpis i pečat i korisnici su brzo ustanovili da je u pitanju lažna vest.', 'False letter of resignation of MP published on Twitter', 'A photo of a false letter of resignation of the Minister of Mining and Energy Dubravka Đedović appeared on Twitter. It was soon discovered that the letter was fabricated and that the Minister did not resign. The signature and seal were missing from the letter and users quickly realized that it was fake news.', '2023-06-08', null, 3, 2, 1, '', '', '', 3, 15, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/andrejic_bojan/status/1666594733622280192', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/XjdYz', '');

VALUES('Glumci i glumice trpe organizovane napade na mrežama', 'U jeku podrške broja glumaca i glumica protestima protiv nasilja koji traju nedeljama, na društvenim mrežama počeli su da cirkulišu sadržaji u kojima se objavljuje koliko novca ove javne ličnosti dobijaju od državnog operatera Telekom Srbija za snimanje serija i filmova u njihovoj produkciji. Ne zna se odakle su ove informacije potekle, ali su napadi na mrežama usledili nakon što su narodni poslanici u Skupštini čitali slične spiskove. ', 'Vice President of the National Assembly targets actor on Twitter for supporting protests', 'Member of the Presidency of the Serbian Progressive Party and Vice-President of the National Assembly, Sandra Božić, attacked actor Milan Marić on Twitter a day after Marić spoke at the "Serbia against violence" protest. Božić called out the actor for his so-called "anti-Serb" views and shared a video in which Marić reads the statements of victims and witnesses of the genocide in Srebrenica from the trial of Radislav Krstić and Ratko Mladić, which was created as part of the Hague Tribunal project. Marić was the target of criticism because of this video before, but after joining the protests, he again attracted the public''s attention.', '2023-06-11', null, 6, 2, 1, '', '', '', 15, 22, 8, 7, 15, 48, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/PrijateljNaroda/status/1667978013093314565', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/g1Pqz', '');

VALUES('Potpresednica Narodne skupštine targetirala glumca na Tviteru zbog podrške protestima', 'Član Predsedništva Srpske napredne stranke i Potpredsednica Narodne skupštine Sandra Božić je na Tviteru napala glumca Milana Marića dan nakon što je Marić govorio na protestu "Srbija protiv nasilja". Božić je prozvala glumca zbog takozvanih "antisrpskih" stavova i podelila video u kojem Marić čita iskaze žrtava i svedoka genocida u Srebrenici sa suđenja Radislavu Krstiću i Ratku Mladiću koji je nastao kao deo projekta Haškog suda. Marić je i ranije zbog ovog videa bio meta kritika, ali je nakon uključenja u proteste ponovo privukao pažnju javnosti. ', 'Serbian Actress and her children received threats on Instagram', 'After she supported the protests, actress Tamara Dragićević received numerous threats on Instagram for weeks. In the most recent messages, commenters told the actress they knew that her children were on a school trip and when they had their recitals. The threats were reported to the police.', '2023-06-10', null, 6, 8, 1, '', '', '', 14, 7, 8, 7, 15, 48, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/BozicSandra/status/1667316490964533248', '', '', '', 'https://archive.ph/8khkt', '');

VALUES('Glumici i njenoj deci upućene pretnje na Instagramu', 'Nakon što je podržala proteste, glumici Tamari Dragićević nedeljama su stizale mnogobrojne pretnje na Instragramu. U poslednjim porukama se glumici poručuje da se zna gde su joj deca otišla na izlet kao i kada imaju završne priredbe. Pretnje su prijavljene policiji. ', 'Nuclear engineer fired because of critical tweets about the government', 'A nuclear engineer was dismissed from the Directorate for Radiation and Nuclear Safety and Security due to her tweets on the account under the pseudonym "Mila Sila". The tweets contained criticism of the behavior of high-ranking state officials, and the engineer was previously targeted by disciplinary measures at the workplace because of her tweets.', '2023-06-10', null, 6, 2, 1, '', '', '', 15, 7, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/p/CtWNWWrsOH5/?igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D', 'https://n1info.rs/vesti/glumici-tamari-dragicevic-stigle-pretnje-zbog-podrske-protestu-spominju-i-decu/', 'https://n1info.rs/vesti/glumici-tamari-dragicevic-stigle-pretnje-zbog-podrske-protestu-spominju-i-decu/', '', '(screenshot)', 'https://archive.li/dtHTT');

VALUES('Nukleana inženjerka dobila otkaz zbog kritičkih tvitova o vlasti', 'Nuklearnoj inžinjerki je zbog tvitova na nalogu pod pseudonimom "Mila Sila" uručen otkaz u Direktoratu za radijacionu i nuklearnu sigurnost i bezbednost. Tvitovi su sadržali kritike ponašanja visokih državnih funkcionera, a inženjerka je zbog tvitova i ranije bila targetirana disciplinskim merama na radnom mestu.', 'Theater receives threats and insults on Twitter', 'The independent theater "Reflektor Teatar" published a Twitter thread about the 90s and the wars in the territory of the former Yugoslavia and invited citizens to share what they know about their parents'' youth. In the responses to their tweets, a large number of insults and threats addressed to the theater followed.', '2023-06-09', null, 3, 3, 1, '', '', '', 8, 9, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.vreme.com/kolumna/slucaj-nuklearne-inzenjerke-otkaz-zbog-politicki-nepodobnih-tvitova/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/sM4nd', '');

VALUES('Pozorište na meti pretnji i uvreda na Tviteru', 'Nezavisno pozorište "Reflektor teatar" je na Tviteru objavilo niz o 90-im godinama i ratovima na prostoru bivše SFRJ i pozvalo građane da podele šta znaju o mladosti svojih roditelja. U odgovorima na njihove tvitove je usledio veliki broj uvreda i pretnji upućenih teatru. ', 'Article about the RTV Managing Board decision removed from media websites', 'An article about the decision of the Management Board od the Radio Television of Vojvodina to appoint a new acting director instead of a new general director has been deleted from the website of that provincial institution. The news was also deleted from other media portals from Vojvodina such as Dnevnik and Vojvodina uživo.', '2023-06-13', null, 1, 4, 1, '', '', '', 15, 7, 8, 7, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/reflektorteatar/status/1668588910253862913?t=eVkbT4EVW__tq_GJSNYfag&s=35', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/kFEbD', '');

VALUES('Vest o odluci Upravnog odbora RTV brisana sa sajtova medija', 'Sa sajta Radio-televizije Vojvodine (RTV) obrisana je vest o odluci Upravog odbora te institucije da umesto izbora novog generalnog direktora imenuje novog vršioca dužnosti te funkcije. Vest je takođe obrisana sa drugih vojvođanskih portala poput Dnevnika i Vojvodina uživo.', 'Popular YouTuber insluts trans person in his livestream', 'A popular YouTuber posted a live stream in which he scrolled through Tinder profiles of girls and commented on them. In the video, he used insults and inappropriate jokes against a trans girl who reported abuse to the organization Da se zna.', '2023-06-21', null, 3, 1, 1, '', '', '', 1, 27, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.cenzolovka.rs/drzava-i-mediji/skandal-oko-izbora-direktora-rtv-nekom-se-odluka-upravnog-odbora-nije-dopala-vest-izbrisana-sa-nekoliko-portala/', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/aLsB5', '');

VALUES('Popularni jutjuber vređao trans osobu u svom lajvstrimu', 'Popularni jutjuber objavio je lajvstrim u kojem je listao Tinder profile devojaka komentarišući ih.  On je u videu iznosio uvrede i neumesne šale na račun trans devojke koja je prijavila zlostavljanje organizaciji Da se zna. ', 'Scam SMS Messages Impersonating Service Providers', 'The National Bank of Serbia warns citizens to be cautious if they receive SMS messages from unknown phone numbers, especially those with the country code +33. The sender falsely presents themselves as a provider of services for companies such as Netflix, Serbian Post, DHL, and similar ones, but it is a scam. The websites linked in the SMS messages are fraudulent.', '2023-06-21', null, 3, 5, 1, '', '', '', 14, 10, 4, 10, 4, 25, 6, 38, 1, 25, 'https://www.instagram.com/p/CttgvTiMaEa/?igshid=MTc4MmM1YmI2Ng%3D%3D', '', '', '', '(screenshot)', '');

VALUES('NBS upozorila na prevare putem SMS-a', 'Narodna banka Srbije upozorava građane da budu oprezni ukoliko dobiju SMS poruke sa nepoznatih brojeva telefona, posebno onih sa pozivnim brojem +33. Pošiljalac se lažno predstavlja kao pružalac usluga za Netflliks, Pošta Srbije, DHL i slično, ali se radi o prevari. Veb stranice koje su linkovne u SMS poruci su lažne.', 'Actors and actresses suffer organized attacks on social media', 'In the wake of the support of a number of actors to the protests against violence that have been going on for weeks, videos began to circulate on social networks announcing how much money these public figures receive from the state operator Telekom Srbija for filming series and movies under their production. It is not known where this information came from, but the attacks on the networks followed after MPs read similar lists in the Parliament.', '2023-06-27', null, 3, 2, 2, '', '', '', 10, 21, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://www.021.rs/story/Info/Srbija/345058/NBS-upozorila-na-SMS-prevaru-Obratite-paznju-na-nepoznate-brojeve.html', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/li9Ff', '');

VALUES('Privatni snimak pevačice okačen na mreže bez saglasnosti', 'Privatni snimak koji je folk pevačica Ana Nikolić poslala Saši Mirković, direktoru Hype televizije, kojem se direktno obraća u videu, objavljen je na društvenim profilima televizijske stanice bez njene saglasnosti. Snimak je podeljen sa opisom u kojem tim televizije implicira da je pevačica, kojoj se očigledno vidi da nije dobro, koristila razne suspstance, i jasno je da je video bio namenjen određenoj osobi i da nije bio za deljenje. Video je brzo počeo da se širi društvenim mrežama i objavljivan je od strane raznih drugih naloga. ', 'Private video of singer posted on social media without her consent', 'A private video that folk singer Ana Nikolić sent to Saša Mirković, the director of Hype Television, whom she addresses directly in the video, was published on the tv station''s social media profiles without her consent. The video was shared with a description in which the television''s social media team implied that the singer, who was visibly unwell in the recording, had been using various substances, and it was clear that the video was intended for a specific person and was not meant to be shared. The video quickly started circulating around social media and was being shared by a number of accounts.', '2023-07-01', null, 6, 5, 1, '', '', '', 14, 19, null, null, null, null, 6, 33, 6, 38, 'https://twitter.com/Sivaeminencija2/status/1675091170932801536?s=20', 'https://twitter.com/Tajniznak26/status/1675093695643648003', 'https://twitter.com/Tajniznak26/status/1675093695643648003', '', '(screenshot 1&2)', '');

VALUES('Sajt regionalnog medija pod tehničkim napadom', 'Sajt Južnih vesti tokom 3. Jula pretrpeo je ozbiljan DDoS napad na njihov sajt. Na sreću posledice su uspešno otklonjene. O napadu su čitaoce obavetili preko Tviter naloga. ', 'The website of a regional media outlet was under a technical attack', 'The website of Južne vesti experienced a severe DDoS attack on July 3rd. Fortunately, the consequences were successfully mitigated. They informed their readers about the attack through their Twitter account.', '2023-07-03', '2023-07-03', 2, 2, 2, '', '', '', 9, 4, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/juznevesti/status/1675874913415049218?t=PgKPl5roQ26kLzBzFL32Kg&s=09', '', '', '', '(screenshot-juznevesti)', '');

VALUES('Transfobija i dednejmovanje ubijene trans devojke na društvenim mrežama', 'Na objavama na društvenim mrežama koje je povodom ubistva trans devojke Noe Milivojev objavila organizacija Da se zna objavljeni su brojni transfobični komentari. U nekim od ovih komentara izvršeno je dednejmovanje Noe, odnosno navođenje njenog imena pre tranzicije.', 'Transphobia and deadnaming of a murdered trans girl on social networks', 'Numerous transphobic comments were published on social media accounts organization Da se zna regarding the murder of trans girl Noa Milivojev. In some of these comments, Noah was deadnamed, i.e. her name before the transition was written. ', '2023-07-06', null, 3, 4, 1, '', '', '', 4, 25, null, null, null, null, 6, 38, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/dasezna/status/1676979327173271552?t=6fy-eoIWOgGolV_rQ_k6tA&s=35', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/KRfCx', '');

VALUES('Spisak botova SNS objavljen na Tviteru, izvor nepoznat', 'Tviter korisnik @protivdictature objavio je spisak naloga koji su navodno botovi Srpske napredne stranke. Spisak sadrži imena, prezimena i mesto prebivalista osobe koja stoji iza naloga kao i sam nalog koji je u pitanju. I dalje nije jasno odakle je spisak potekao, nalog koji je objavio tvrdi da ga je platio i dobio od Sprske napredne stranke. U danima nakon što je spisak objavljen, drugi korisnici Tvitera tvrdili su da su pronašli svoje poznanike i članove porodica na spiskovima, neki su objavljivali informacije o radnim mestima nekih i u nekim slučajevima je navedeno da su ljudi sa spiskova pretrpeli fizičko nasilje.', 'List of SNS bot accounts published on Twitter, source unknown', 'Twitter user @protivdictature published a list of accounts that are allegedly bots of the Serbian Progressive Party. The list contains the names, surnames and city of the person behind the account as well as the account in question. It is still not clear where the list came from, the account he published claims he paid for it and received it from the Serbian Progressive Party. In the days after the list was published, other Twitter users claimed to have found acquaintances and family members on the lists and in some cases stated that people on the lists had suffered physical violence.', '2023-07-06', null, 7, 10, 3, '', '', '', 7, 20, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/protivdictature/status/1677054817649213440?s=46', '', '', '', 'https://archive.li/BWQHF', '');

VALUES('Žene sa spiska botova na mrežama našle su se na meti mizoginih komentara i pretnji ', 'Veliki broj slika i ličnih podataka ljudi čija imena su se nalašla na spisku botova koji je objavljen 06. jula na Tviteru je u prethodnim danima bio izložen raznim verbalnim napadima i pretnjama na mrežama. Ženske osobe sa ovih spiskova su se pored opštih napada našle i na meti mizoginih i uvredljivih komentara koji su rodno zasnovani više nego išta. ', 'Women from the bot list are targeted with misogynistic comments and threats on social media', 'A large number of pictures and personal data of people whose names were on the list of bots published on July 6 on Twitter were exposed to various verbal attacks and threats on the networks in the previous days. In addition to general attacks, women from these lists have also been the target of misogynistic and offensive comments that are more gender-based than anything else.', '2023-07-10', null, 3, 4, 1, '', '', '', 4, 22, 4, 25, null, null, 4, 29, 6, 38, 'https://twitter.com/MisoIlic032/status/1678506098171555840?s=20', 'https://twitter.com/kaldrma70/status/1678479739944681474?s=20', 'https://twitter.com/kaldrma70/status/1678479739944681474?s=20', '', 'https://archive.li/IqSmY', 'https://archive.ph/fd0vH');

VALUES('Kreator iskoristio intimni snimak pevačice bez saglasnosti za promociju svog sadržaja', 'Istok Pavlović objavio je na svom TikToku video u kojem je koristio sliku iz intimnog videa pevačice Severine Vučković iz 2004. godine kako bi demonstrirao mogućnosti novih AI alata u fotošopu. Nakon što je video naišao na negodovanje na mrežama, Pavlović je objavio objašnjenje gde se nije izvinio, već pokušao da opravda korišćenje fotografije. ', 'Creator used singer''s intimate recording without consent to promote his content', 'Content creator Istok Pavlović posted a video on his TikTok in which he used an image from an intimate video of singer Severina Vučković from 2004 to demonstrate the possibilities of new AI tools in Photoshop. After the video was met with outrage on the networks, Pavlović published an explanation where he did not apologize, but tried to justify the use of the photo.', '2023-07-09', null, 6, 5, 1, '', '', '', 14, 40, null, null, null, null, 6, 33, null, null, 'https://twitter.com/preputiumpenis/status/1678143335226044420?s=46', '', '', '', 'https://archive.ph/mg5Ux', '');

